{"id": 3028, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中的哪些时刻会让你觉得「大脑有时真的很不靠谱」？", "description": "你都会在什么情况下觉得「自己好像被大脑忽悠了」？（题图来自：iStock ©️ ussr）", "record_count": 1639, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191013230331THWO3ZLN4gb1tJAi.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-15T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 348418, "content": "12:30我就眯一会就一刻钟\n14:00哎哟，睡得真香", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609123}, {"id": 348419, "content": "被人打岔之后突然忘记自己刚刚要做什么的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139842}, {"id": 348426, "content": "出门：哎我东西忘带了\n进门：我要拿什么来着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268843}, {"id": 348428, "content": "每次背题……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667297}, {"id": 348691, "content": "上课明明听懂了觉得哦哦原来是这样\n晚上写作业脑子里一片空白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570569}, {"id": 348698, "content": "和同事聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479706}, {"id": 348444, "content": "时间明明已经逝去，却仿佛还是生活在昨天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428610}, {"id": 348445, "content": "媳妇儿身份证号多少来着？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667317}, {"id": 348446, "content": "想象太快，经常听别人说话听到一半就已经联想到别的东西了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001167}, {"id": 348447, "content": "终是忘记接下来要干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571101}, {"id": 348451, "content": "经常讲一句话，发现有几个字是颠倒了顺序的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667356}, {"id": 348453, "content": "你以为爱情到来的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981010}, {"id": 348455, "content": "刚想好要去做一件事的时候\n起身准备去做就忘记了要干啥。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665667}, {"id": 348457, "content": "本来知道有方法，但还是陷入一个情绪区里出不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667350}, {"id": 348458, "content": "考试开始的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605111}, {"id": 348460, "content": "记不清路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659809}, {"id": 348461, "content": "刚锁上门，我锁门了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824931}, {"id": 348462, "content": "我关门了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667400}, {"id": 348742, "content": "在我减肥的时候他总是突然想喝奶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668116}, {"id": 348749, "content": "我忘了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667865}, {"id": 348752, "content": "对一个人有好感的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447988}, {"id": 348245, "content": "明明觉得也没玩多久手机，一看都过去好几个小时了", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348246, "content": "想睡觉时，脑海里却会不受控制地重复白天听到的抖音神曲", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348247, "content": "虽然不喜欢洗脑广告，但购物时却会不由自主地选这个牌子", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348515, "content": "有印象去过一个地方，看到一个熟悉的人，经历过一件事，然而并没有发生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667507}, {"id": 348793, "content": "不知道自己写啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668383}, {"id": 349054, "content": "那个叫什么来着？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1669271}, {"id": 349072, "content": "站在人行通道上看到绿灯亮了，然后说红灯，赶紧过……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1669423}, {"id": 348562, "content": "回答问题的时候。", "image": "img/option/option/20191020171031OHP0KpZR7axsAoJ9", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579765}, {"id": 348833, "content": "考试的时候脑子里会开始循环刚听过的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619862}, {"id": 348327, "content": "合上书 准备默写的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 359, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376867}, {"id": 348330, "content": "分不清做过的梦和现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537367}, {"id": 348331, "content": "考试的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377475}, {"id": 348332, "content": "暗恋一个人的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666991}, {"id": 348333, "content": "大脑不能控制冲动^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473258}, {"id": 348334, "content": "记忆混乱的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665736}, {"id": 348336, "content": "输取件码要低头看三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247205}, {"id": 348337, "content": "一闲下来就会自动接入负面记忆网络", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625938}, {"id": 348338, "content": "爱上一个人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612661}, {"id": 348339, "content": "看过的书不记得的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489025}, {"id": 348340, "content": "上一秒说的话，下一秒忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443036}, {"id": 348341, "content": "剁手的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334072}, {"id": 348597, "content": "关上门的瞬间想起没带钥匙🔑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182393}, {"id": 348343, "content": "睡觉的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577415}, {"id": 348345, "content": "我还没吃饱", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173340}, {"id": 348346, "content": "才阅读了半个小时，就想睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927839}, {"id": 348347, "content": "回想刚刚做过的梦的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430193}, {"id": 348348, "content": "看见美女就有性冲动", "image": "img/option/option/20191016091614vI9X2fQB8A6WwUzc.png", "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 13823}, {"id": 348604, "content": "我明明记得！", "image": "img/option/option/20191021093836v5JG6cTVyzMruW3U.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667743}, {"id": 348349, "content": "一准备去健身就提醒我哪里不舒服哪里还有事没做完", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323702}]}